  "texts": [
    "Although such enhancement methods are able to expand the dataset to some extent, they still have some limitations, such as the dependence on the existing image base and the limited enhancement effect.",
    "Moreover, another feasible method for dataset generation is based on text-to-image synthesis.",
    "For instance, cGANs (conditional Generative Adversarial Networks) 25, VAEs (Variational Auto-Encoders) 26, and the Stable Diffusion 27 model have achieved remarkable success in generating high-quality images.",
    "Despite the theoretically powerful generative capabilities of these models, there is limited detailed research in the literature regarding their application in dataset generation.",
    "The primary obstacle lies in the significant demand for extensive textual descriptions, posing a challenge for researchers to generate sufficiently rich descriptions in practice."
  ],
